data.name: Label5.Text
data.value: Additional Info: From the generated report, you may click the icon with a single arrow located in the upper left of the window, which symbolizes for “Export” button, to save a softcopy of the report. Click the double arrow icon to refresh the generate report. Click the exit button to go back to the report window.

data.name: Label2.Text
data.value: 2. Filter the list by setting the date of the specific record that you want to view or print and click “Search” button. Click “Refresh” button to remove the filter of the list. Click “Print” button to generate the report.
